        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1945-11-27T19:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1944-07-17T00:00:00-05:00" n="295" subtype="editorial-note" type="document" xml:id="d295">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>No record of the substance of this meeting has been found. <persName corresp="#p_CWS1">Churchill</persName> had his quarters in H. M. S. <hi rend="italic">Orion</hi> in Grand Harbor, Malta. The information given here
                    as to the meeting and the participants is taken from <persName corresp="#p_CWS1">Churchill</persName>, <ref target="#pg_343">p. 343</ref>.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
